name: Unicorn (Ps. A Random Thoughts Collection)
description: Whatever, and whoever you are. It don't matter. We believe what we believe for. We are magical and mythical creatures, we just do what are we needed to do. Sometimes we don't know that we are already doing what's impossible, we just only care that we are always staying the same path, stay focus. It's a lonely path, you already know what it is.
